ReadME


To Create an AWS Security group using Terraform and attach to instance | security group tf code


# 1st Step need to create EC2 Instance 


# 2nd Step create Security Groups
Define 3 ingress and 1 egress rules and create it


3rd Step Need to assign the earlier created Security Group to the EC2 which has created earlier and need to define it under instance_type like.
security_groups = [aws_security_group.TF_SG.name] the SG name is TF_SG

before that need to check using below commands
# terraform validate
# terraform plan
# terraform apply -auto-approve


Thanks
